The paper deals with communication with fidelity criteria, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also discusses multi-user communication, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also uses a layered black-box view-point, which is a concept in data structures (cs.DS) and discusses the optimality of separation, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
